OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780419953
OL,3,CAvon and Somerset Police being
OL,4,Cinvestigated over house explosion
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct has begun an investigation
OL,9,Finto the contact Avon and Somerset
OL,10,FPolice had with Joanne Shaw and Ryan
OL,11,FKelly prior to their deaths in
OL,12,FFrenchay.
OL,14,FThey both died following an explosion
OL,15,Fat a property on Sterncourt Road, in
OL,16,Fthe Frenchay area of Bristol, on 3 May
OL,17,F2026.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
