FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780419953
OL,3,CAvon and Somerset Police being
OL,4,Cinvestigated over house explosion
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FFollowing a mandatory referral from
OL,8,Fthe force, the IOPC is investigating
OL,9,Fprior contact police had with Ms Shaw
OL,10,Fand Mr Kelly. Police last had contact
OL,11,Fwith Ms Shaw four days before the
OL,12,Fexplosion.
OL,14,FThe investigation will look at whether
OL,15,Fappropriate steps were taken by police
OL,16,Fto safeguard Ms Shaw before she died,
OL,17,Fspanning a timeframe of five years,
OL,18,Fbetween May 2021 and May 2026,
OL,19,Fincluding whetherallincidentsduring
OL,20,Fthis periodwere adequately resourced,
OL,21,Fprogressed and risk assessed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780419953
OL,3,CAvon and Somerset Police being
OL,4,Cinvestigated over house explosion
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe IOPC said it will also look at
OL,8,Fwhether there were any missed
OL,9,Fopportunities which may have
OL,10,Fcontributed to the deaths of Ms Shaw
OL,11,Fand Mr Kelly and whether police
OL,12,Fofficers and staff acted in accordance
OL,13,Fwith local and national policies and
OL,14,Fprocedures.
OL,16,FIOPC Director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,17,F"My thoughts and sympathies are with
OL,18,Feveryone affected at this very
OL,19,Fdifficult time.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
