OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780419953
OL,3,CAvon and Somerset Police being
OL,4,Cinvestigated over house explosion
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"We are independent of the police and
OL,8,Fit is important that we carry out a
OL,9,Fthorough investigation, to fully
OL,10,Festablish the circumstances of what
OL,11,Fhappened prior to the tragic events of
OL,12,F3 May. There is a significant history
OL,13,Fof police involvement in relation to
OL,14,FMr Kelly's behaviour, including
OL,15,Fallegations of stalking, harassment
OL,16,Fand assault, which we need to examine
OL,17,Fas part of our investigation.
OL,19,F"We are reviewing extensive
OL,20,Fdocumentation detailing that history
OL,21,Fas part of our enquiries
OL,26,@oD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
