OL,3,CAvon and Somerset Police being
OL,4,Cinvestigated over house explosion
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"We will be keeping all interested
OL,8,Fparties updated as our investigation,
OL,9,Fwhich is at an early stage,
OL,10,Fprogresses."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@LO]
